    "name": "Mesh independence study — VAD centrifugal pump geometry",
    "description": "Systematic mesh refinement study conducted on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under VAD operating conditions (3500–5500 RPM, 2–8 L/min). Four mesh densities (coarse: 1.2M cells, medium: 4.8M cells, fine: 11.4M cells, extra-fine: 24.1M cells) were evaluated. Grid convergence index (GCI) was computed per ASME V&V 20 guidelines. Target GCI < 2% on hemolysis index QoI. Activity performed using ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 with double-precision solver on HPC cluster.",
