      "rationale": "Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model used. Model form uncertainty is large and well-documented in literature (factor of 2–3 variation in predicted nIH across published coefficient sets). No mechanistic RBC damage model employed. Model form uncertainty not formally quantified in this assessment. Achieved level 2 against required level 5 — largest credibility gap."
