    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed. Seven factors show achieved levels below required levels, with the largest gaps in Model Form (achieved 2, required 5) and Use Error (achieved 1, required 3). Six factors have significant shortfalls. Monte Carlo UQ performed but uncertainty bands remain too wide for absolute hemolysis threshold acceptance at Class III MRL 5. Mesh independence verification activity declared but GCI evidence not linked in package. Overall credibility insufficient for regulatory submission without remediation of model form uncertainty and independent verification of mesh convergence evidence.",
